{"tid":1624329,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「十一」爆笑料！花車由人力推動？逾千學生熬高溫當「後備動力」","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:49:06.000Z","uid":35519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7879886faf328e2003aea08c82dae41d480ce9","tid":1624329,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「十一」爆笑料！<br />\n閱兵花車由人力推動？<br />\n逾千學生熬高溫當「後備動力」</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網民嘲：這是不是傳說中的「人工智能」啊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAyN3ER.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAyN3ER.jpg&h=d7737e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2NphGFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NphGFT.jpg&h=96b2c43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">【新唐人北京時間2019年10月04日訊】</span></em><br />\n10月1號上午，在中共建政70週年彩車遊行的方陣中，先後有31個省、直轄市、自治區等的70組花車參演，很多人以為這些緩緩行駛的花車，只有一名司機在駕駛，但有網友爆料，這些花車的內部，暗藏上千名大學生作為動力「備胎」。<br />\n<br />\n據《天天快報》報導，有知道內幕的網友爆料說：遊行的花車雖然是電動的，但為了應急，專門配備了1700多名大學生推車人員，<strong><ins>他們藏身在車裡面，灰塵多、溫度高、噪音大，還訓練了好久，爆料人還說：這主要是為「省錢」</ins></strong>。還有網民表示：官方是怕動力出故障，以防萬一用人力保障，但這群學生練了一個暑假，雖然在現場但卻什麼都看不到。<br />\n<br />\n陝西的花車就被網民披露雖然投入巨資，卻時好時壞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gN8KmqD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgN8KmqD.jpg&h=729f463a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lijingdepengyou/posts/2443308832422004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flijingdepengyou%2Fposts%2F2443308832422004&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqjbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=c58659f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lijingdepengyou/posts/2443308832422004</a>"},{"pid":"198f56d75e5ad4198407d368a365d6131b431c84","tid":1624329,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"消息曝光後，海外社交平台推特上響起一片嘲笑聲，比如：<br />\n<br />\n「開眼了！這是不是傳說中的人工智能？」<br />\n<br />\n「用電動車怕出故障，所以用土辦法。不管用什麼，都是土鱉式的閱兵。」<br />\n<br />\n但有網友有不同的看法。大陸網友陳先生：「說那個花車是人力，用常理來說省油錢這個也理由不成立的，大學生擱那個花車嘛，一天一百塊。國慶閱兵我反感這個，因為沒有意義，浪費納稅人錢，完全拒絕去了解、去談。」<br />\n<br />\n更多的是海外的批評聲：「<strong><ins>香港學生上街拉人鏈，為自由！大陸學生上街拉花車，當馬牛！</ins></strong>」，橫批：<ins>一國兩智</ins>。[/b]<br />\n<br />\n還有大陸網友表示，香港的學生生活在自由民主的環境，接受的是世界文明的教育和薰陶，而大陸的學生接受的是中共洗腦教育的。<br />\n<br />\n大陸匿名網友：「用人力代替機器，顯示的就是有這麼多被洗腦的同胞願意參與，享受這種假繁華下的這種盛事的狂歡，大陸的這些學生，他所受到洗腦的教育、愚民的教育，他沒有整個世界文明之類的格局和胸懷，沒有為人民的長久的利益去獻身這種精神。」"},{"pid":"4c0627cc6e3391881cb409921e5b53c1c1430d3a","tid":1624329,"uid":35519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUQgWVh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUQgWVh.jpg&h=d2f66e0a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGKtN2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGKtN2u.jpg&h=c569ae65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸網友唐先生：「他們還感覺到很榮幸，他們就覺得國家強盛，所以中國的教育已經爛透了，把這些學生全部通過洗腦成同一個模式，真的很悲哀。香港的學生爭取自己的最基本的權利，這個我們還是感到很驕傲的。」<br />\n<br />\n大陸網友唐先生表示，他為大陸學生感到悲哀，為香港學生感到驕傲，因為他看到香港學生有世界觀、有擔當、不畏強權，堅持爭取民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/mkt_ipad/2019/10/04/a102678969.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2Fmkt_ipad%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2Fa102678969.html&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqjbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=61145a6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/mkt_ipad/2019/10/04/a102678969.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.aboluowang.com/2019/1004/1351426.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2019%2F1004%2F1351426.html&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqjbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=eba2275b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.aboluowang.com/2019/1004/1351426.html</a>"},{"pid":"4916971caceeea64529784f66dc138c1630eabe6","tid":1624329,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81947fcb5a20b96494c272b046026051bc0de47","tid":1624329,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a34c5cbd601fd7c8c3ec1a05edb926359c3cb08","tid":1624329,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c81947fcb5a20b96494c272b046026051bc0de47","tid":1624329,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea874993e694bbb031d7be02b30fd6d32108c3fb","tid":1624329,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}